      <h2>COFFEE COVID CHEER</h2> 
      As the novel coronavirus sweeps the globe, countries around the globe watch as COVID-19 cases and coffee consumption influence their happiness rankings. 
    </p>
    
    <h2>What inspired 3 C's?</h2>
    
      <p>
        A <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ"><b>2023 TJHSST study*</b></a> found astounding correlations between coffee consumption, COVID-19 cases, and happiness levels for countries around the globe on planet Earth. 
        <ul>
          <li>Those who drink coffee are 13% less likely to transmit COVID-19 to others. </li>
          <li>Having COVID-19 makes one half as likely to discuss happiness with others.</li>
          <li>Living near a coffee shop makes an individual 2.6 times as likely to accidentally leave their mask in their car. </li>
          <li>63% of coffee drinkers happily drink caramel macchiatos.</li>
          <li>Dr. Fauci is experimenting with coffee beans in the production of his next happiness vaccine. </li>
          
          
        </ul>
      </p>
  
   <h2>What does 3 C's do?</h2>
    <p>3 C's is a website that connects COVID-19, coffee, and cheerfulness. Using machine learning techniques, we find a correlation between 
        <ul>
          <li>the amount of coffee consumed by a country</li>
          <li>the prevalance of COVID-19 in a country</li>
          <li>& happiness rankings in a country.</li>
          
          
        </ul>
    </p>
    
         
